{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"建構子","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Constructor","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>建構子（<strong>constructor</strong>）屬於實做（instantiated）的指定 class <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Object\">object</a>。建構子概念可應用到大多數的<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/OOP\">物件導向</a>程式語言。基本上，<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/JavaScript\">JavaScript</a> 建構子用於在 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Class\">class</a> 的實做（instance）聲明。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"語法","title":"語法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// 這是個通用的建構子 class Default</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Default</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 這是擁有幾個參數的過載建構子 class Overloaded</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Overloaded</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">arg1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> arg2<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>argN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>要呼叫 JavaScript 內的建構子 class ，請用 <code>new</code> 操作符給 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Variable\">variable <small>(en-US)</small></a> 宣告新的 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Object_reference\">object reference <small>(en-US)</small></a>。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Default</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 新的 Default 物件參照被分派給局部變數 defaultReference</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> defaultReference <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Default</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"深入理解","title":"深入理解","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本知識","title":"基本知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>維基百科的 <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%A7%8B%E9%80%A0%E5%99%A8\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">構造器</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技術資訊","title":"技術資訊","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>MDN 的 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/JavaScript/Objects#the_constructor\">JavaScript 物件導向介紹</a></li>\n  <li>MDN 的 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/new\">JavaScript 的 new 操作符</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"語法","id":"語法"},{"text":"深入理解","id":"深入理解"}],"summary":"建構子（constructor）屬於實做（instantiated）的指定 class object。建構子概念可應用到大多數的物件導向程式語言。基本上，JavaScript 建構子用於在 class 的實做（instance）聲明。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Constructor","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Constructor","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Constructeur","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Constructor (コンストラクター)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Конструктор","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Constructor","locale":"zh-CN","